{
  "texts": [
    "The evaluation of the usefulness of the AI tools can distinguish between experienced military analysts and students without professional experience.",
    "It can therefore be assumed that experienced military analysts perceive the added value of using AI tools even more strongly.",
    "It should also be noted that AI is still in a massive development phase.",
    "For example, the limitations in the use of NER identified in the study due to incorrect tagging may have been improved since the time of the study.",
    "Finally, it should be noted that due to the design of the study, it is not possible to make statements about the AI functions individually, as their added value was only analyzed in combination."
  ]
}